  "title": "Coze 2.5 发布：成为 Agent 的网络",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&mid=2247515172&idx=1&sn=f5dc5404f8a2c7fb163125dfd54e89c9",
  "date": "2026-04-07 06:02:00",
  "author": "赛博禅心",
  "siteName": "赛博禅心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b5e91828&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FjXSGuwJvpdiaeVnkMCI19vq0RFsqRGPEJOL7B0Dv2Ge0r9c5TxdVxWFcdWSxHRxFvaeZWdwDwFoTQxkCerwBKJu3IfKAAyWhsRQwoJibdC2a0%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>独立身份、工具链、Agent World... all in one</p>\n  <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.02);padding:0;\">\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px 16px 12px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#cf4436;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">PRODUCT</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px 16px 16px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天 Coze 2.5 发布，这个版本给每个 Agent 建了独立身份（</span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">@coze.email</span></code><span leaf=\"\">），让 Agent 能够相互交流，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(207, 68, 54);font-weight: bold;\">构建了一整张 Agent 网络</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 8px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">今晚，我也会和朋克周一起，在 Coze 官方直播间，聊一下这个 Coze 2.5</span></span></p>\n    <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-videosnap class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card channels_live_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpvideosnap\" data-headimgurl=\"https://wx.qlogo.cn/finderhead/FMajU52WvbFOfawfuic0mJYTmZicuhhOhicPU1XODJd3TbCicokh5E0MibeNuL5CdC6ZIsFZ0wYBx1nI/0\" data-username=\"v2_060000231003b20faec8c4e58f1ec2ddcd02ec30b07719146ed837593a1cd448596df15da2d5@finder\" data-nickname=\"扣子Coze\" data-desc=\"将在04月07日 19:00 直播\" data-type=\"live\" data-intro=\"扣子全新升级！大咖带你满配开箱\" data-noticeid=\"finderlivenotice-v2_060000231003b20faec8c4e58f1ec2ddcd02ec30b07719146ed837593a1cd448596df15da2d5@finder-1775202929155028-1978428925\" data-status=\"0\"></mp-common-videosnap></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文也将会从四个层面，来说说 Coze 的这个 Agent 网络：</span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent 的身份</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，</span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">围绕身份的工具链</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，</span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent 网络</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，以及为什么整个行业都在</span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">往类似的方向探索</span></code></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"362\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdjkMN7YozdvqUaMuKrib6NswoHsphNjXbKpX55bjMCSKNBIlWkGDviaZrVj25e0EHIU3S9BwQzmwxEscjp6gQQnFsNzic938vysS8/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"362\" data-imgfileid=\"100031481\" data-ratio=\"0.6629213483146067\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2314\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2c7a18c5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdjkMN7YozdvqUaMuKrib6NswoHsphNjXbKpX55bjMCSKNBIlWkGDviaZrVj25e0EHIU3S9BwQzmwxEscjp6gQQnFsNzic938vysS8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">有了邮箱和 Agent World，Agent 可以在网络世界中自主探索、学习、连接</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px 8px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent 的身份</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">每个 Agent 分配了一个&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">@coze.email</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的专属邮箱，前缀自定义</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6459016393442623\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2440\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdhYbPiadicz6A6BgbmhCV3tHvPMicd1pE7WUoN4TrG28w5kCuGs58TVpRiaDXQia7ZibeibHb9eVK4DZiaze1icI8AZh2h5yTfVcaEUGibWo/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"353\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"353\" data-imgfileid=\"100031485\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ca1dadfb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdhYbPiadicz6A6BgbmhCV3tHvPMicd1pE7WUoN4TrG28w5kCuGs58TVpRiaDXQia7ZibeibHb9eVK4DZiaze1icI8AZh2h5yTfVcaEUGibWo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">以前 Agent 没有自己的身份，所有操作挂在人类用户名下。帮你注册网站，用的是你的邮箱。在第三方平台产生的数据，混在你的个人数据里。你和 Agent 的边界是模糊的</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在边界清楚了。我把发票丢给扣子处理，开票留的邮箱就是它的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">@coze.email</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。发票信息进它的收件箱，不经过我的个人邮箱。它在飞书上建的文档、在第三方网站注册的账号，都绑在它自己的身份下面，和我的个人账号隔离</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"336\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdgCXmNicKRmFGOSvSjxHLwibddAN4LhSS4eYJBjkBJjgoUQKuic8IPfmYSnoP9gfibsU1h8yuL0czBy9FPKASiayVNPM10tKB7QjK2o/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"362\" data-imgfileid=\"100031497\" data-ratio=\"0.6161417322834646\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2032\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f93fa196&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdgCXmNicKRmFGOSvSjxHLwibddAN4LhSS4eYJBjkBJjgoUQKuic8IPfmYSnoP9gfibsU1h8yuL0czBy9FPKASiayVNPM10tKB7QjK2o%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如我可以让他帮我处理邮箱里的发票</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent 之间可以互发邮件。做完一份数据分析，直接发给另一个 Agent 去写报告，不用人在中间转发</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">微信也接上了。扫码绑定后通过 ClawBot 和扣子对话，记忆和网页端同步</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">我之前做过一个类似的东西，想解决的问题一样：Agent 跨平台时身份怎么统一，信任怎么建立，通信走什么协议。邮箱大概是目前最合理的切入点。人类世界运行了几十年的去中心化身份协议，所有平台都认，所有系统都能对接</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:8px 16px 16px;\">\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(207,68,54,0.06);border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#cf4436;line-height:1.9;margin:0;text-align:center;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">设备和技能让 Agent 更能干，身份让 Agent 成为网络里的一个节点</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:16px 16px 32px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">围绕身份的工具链</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent 有了身份之后，要让它真的能用这个身份去干活，需要给它配一套工具链</span></p>\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">独立的计算环境</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent 用自己的身份注册了飞书，总得有地方打开飞书。云电脑是一台 Ubuntu，有浏览器、文件系统和终端，保留登录态。云手机是一台 Android 13（2vCPU，6GB 内存，45GB 存储），跑原生 App</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"561\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdjnCSP9fSnxBjuc1hm0iaXxLf3WV28ZKR2uTkx2kQjEicBxjE6fv5uxoPtfTyvx1qaYia1y2mL0YlnJ2EVocpa9hDibp2BFCsqt4Dg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"410\" data-imgfileid=\"100031492\" data-ratio=\"1.0266666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=79863899&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdjnCSP9fSnxBjuc1hm0iaXxLf3WV28ZKR2uTkx2kQjEicBxjE6fv5uxoPtfTyvx1qaYia1y2mL0YlnJ2EVocpa9hDibp2BFCsqt4Dg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">这两台设备属于 Agent 自己。它在上面登录的账号、保存的 cookie、下载的文件，都绑在它的身份下面</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6398687448728466\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2438\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdh1ovOo2ia53bbk0J3gsHfCBKV0AxzA00qItmzP7CPKwoAHSFyXblTCicYyictrbIicQiboohIyic9u2ibjGxz9P39oOZ1udfCQkTLSkg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"349\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"349\" data-imgfileid=\"100031494\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=afe26c52&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdh1ovOo2ia53bbk0J3gsHfCBKV0AxzA00qItmzP7CPKwoAHSFyXblTCicYyictrbIicQiboohIyic9u2ibjGxz9P39oOZ1udfCQkTLSkg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">扣子用自己的云电脑打开飞书建多维表格，弹二维码让我扫码授权</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">两者后台异步运行，派完任务继续聊天，做完通知你。需要人介入的操作弹确认框。云手机支持实时屏幕推流，随时能看到 Agent 在做什么</span></p>\n    <h3 style=\"margin:28px 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">可积累的能力</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">技能商店目前&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">365</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;个工具，覆盖开发、办公、自媒体、金融、法律、教育。Agent 装上一个技能，这个技能跟着它的身份走，下次对话还在。多个技能串联使用。你也可以把自己做的技能上架，设免费或收费</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6398687448728466\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2438\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdjZIEicWYib8H6BVqYoBxibEEmBZS3LcJrfaYftEH7qBq3KkDqwCDAt7wXtyvJic3YTOYBibzwsuE29JMibl3vqOejw0vge2IUvZBv4k/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"349\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"349\" data-imgfileid=\"100031495\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=878204d0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdjZIEicWYib8H6BVqYoBxibEEmBZS3LcJrfaYftEH7qBq3KkDqwCDAt7wXtyvJic3YTOYBibzwsuE29JMibl3vqOejw0vge2IUvZBv4k%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">扣子编程让 Agent 自主写代码，视频创作支持 Seedance 2.0，剧本到成片全流程，素材存入资产库跨项目复用</span></p>\n    <h3 style=\"margin:28px 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">持久的记忆</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">跟你聊过的内容不能每次从零开始。记忆系统跨飞书、微信、网页同步，各渠道对话独立但记忆共享，严格按 Session 隔离。短期实时写入，长期由独立 Agent 异步归档，支持向量检索。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4486391571553995\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2278\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdgbj0XWwxMaspPxHAYkyibHurp1eFsjRwhG